Package: nowcast
Type: Package
Title: SIBYL Nowcast / Nearcast Layer
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R:
    person("David", "Stephan", email = "david.stephan@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Bridge equations and simple time-series models (via fable) that
    produce Q+0 and Q+1 estimates for the variables MARTIN needs as a
    handover. Deliberately simple - defensible rather than state-of-the-art.
